about.summary: A helper tool for running array jobs on an HPC computational node.

name: qarrayrun
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "qarrayrun" %}
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 80441f5a0cf27e3ba8805ced549f27c176f43d356e6d783c33ef643585a106c5

build:
  number: 0
  entry_points:
    - qarrayrun = qarrayrun.cli:main
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - pytest-runner
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - qarrayrun
  commands:
    - qarrayrun --help
  requires:
    - pytest

about:
  home: "https://github.com/CFSAN-Biostatistics/qarrayrun"
  license: "BSD"
  license_family: "BSD"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "A helper tool for running array jobs on an HPC computational node."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dpryan79
